						<summary>

						<p>On a slab in a field about a furlong from the Dōṇikavva temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 15th century.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to the god Śrīpatidēva by a son of Śrīdharāchārya, whose name is not mentioned.</p>						

